gnokii provides tools and a user space driver for use with mobile phones
under various operating systems (most testing is done under Linux but
also Solaris, *BSD family and MS Windows families are known to work.

gnokii allows you to communicate with the phone over the serial cable
connection, usb connection (support depends mostly on the operating
system level support), infrared connection, and bluetooth connection.

gnokii provides the functionality of several different areas for users
to manipulate a mobile phone:

* SMS   * Phonebook   * Calendar   * Call management   * others
